{"tid":1663114,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【重申】如有阻膠，要照打！","createTime":"2019-10-19T08:10:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-19T08:28:34.000Z","uid":55378,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"57b6cb778f817a08857046bcf835b800ace31e47","tid":1663114,"uid":55378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T08:10:45.000Z","msg":"阻膠永遠只會阻自己人，對家用暴力就走都走唔切<br />\n思想停留係平衡時空唔緊要，但唔好用行動阻自己友啊嘛<br />\n所以阻膠基本上唔太屬於自己人，可以照打<br />\n最多就唔太重手，但都要足夠令佢地好似班藍屍咁學乖！"},{"pid":"a6b1a84978a563012c59757f0a2a0be34a8ad933","tid":1663114,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T08:10:52.000Z","msg":"【1020 尖咀見】真。遊行指南參考<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/aksjJwU\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/aksjJwU</a>"},{"pid":"9a439afe1696351c6d142cbf1ea25a1b00d46744","tid":1663114,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T08:12:53.000Z","msg":"講咗十萬九千幾次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d63e3a72b13568fe5121a27f85ce211b2a0845d0","tid":1663114,"uid":258706,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T08:13:28.000Z","msg":"先拉走佢<br />\n始終係自己友<br />\n好頑劣咁反抗先再打"},{"pid":"c0216dd52c8f3db87d60afba9ce2dd747afc5fb2","tid":1663114,"uid":95102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T08:13:32.000Z","msg":"提大家今日有咩活動 10 &middot; 19<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n-----------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>全日 全民宣傳日</strong></span> <br />\n- 宣傳1020民陣大遊行<br />\n日期：10月20日<br />\n時間： 1330 <br />\n地點：梳士巴利花園<br />\n[ 各區宣傳，嗌口號，貼文宣，Airdrop ]<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>1900 - 2030 國際人道救援祈禱會</strong></span><br />\n- 愛丁堡廣場<br />\n[已獲不反對通知書]"},{"pid":"d161e4336ffe32f0de560f43e8d0578104c3b640","tid":1663114,"uid":106336,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T08:14:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/J0cUANL.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJ0cUANL.gif&h=e7a459e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n咁樣已足夠"},{"pid":"ae97511bb57449fed6b2cf4b86e74e6460d3905c","tid":1663114,"uid":26952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T08:15:41.000Z","msg":"明天見<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BSSJhsF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBSSJhsF.png&h=a75a6d4c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"382461d5ba328299c1e9cd36b19134f2e933c237","tid":1663114,"uid":94093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d161e4336ffe32f0de560f43e8d0578104c3b640","tid":1663114,"uid":106336,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T08:14:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/J0cUANL.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJ0cUANL.gif&h=e7a459e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n咁樣已足夠"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T08:21:58.000Z","msg":"正確"},{"pid":"f1236337b5d096fc42ab2626f2755e69bf0db591","tid":1663114,"uid":268123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T08:28:34.000Z","msg":"【香城施政報告2019】群策群力 轉危為機<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1656908\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1656908</a><br />\n<br />\n<em><strong>政治問題</strong></em><br />\n<br />\n- 重塑公民身分戶口政策保障國家、香港安全和利益<br />\n- 取消18區區議會、建立地域市政議會<br />\n- 禁止公務人員在任前、任內和任後獲港外榮典<br />\n- 改善高鐵一地兩檢操作方式<br />\n<br />\n<em><strong>便民基建</strong></em><br />\n<br />\n- 興建東鐵、西鐵快速線並完善輕鐵和西鐵聯乘關係<br />\n- 完善機場集體運輸並加強機場、港珠澳大橋協同發展<br />\n- 修正港鐵、巴士可加可減機制<br />\n<br />\n<em><strong>醫療、教育方向</strong></em><br />\n<br />\n- 興建至少四所新區域全科醫院<br />\n- 以減少送院為目標的社區護理服務<br />\n- 重塑教育, 著重知識、技能層次分工<br />\n<br />\n求正評及幫推！"}]}